Final Logo
The logo design is a challenging part because the logo determines the overall
design direction. The logo has to convey the main message of the brand,
show its character, and support its goal. Thus, creating a logo and an icon is a
time-consuming process.
The first idea use an analogy of a career path, it conveys the idea of a fast
career growth. Another idea is to use the arrow in conjunction with a path, sort
of a line connecting two points, as this would stand for the career path.
Logo
BEYOND JOBS
BEYOND JOBS
Experteer logo remain in the same typographic style and color (no
modifications), the Beyond Jobs logo works in conjunction with the Experteer
logo. Green dots shows a future feeling which means Beyond Jobs utilises
Artificial Intelligence to predict your career path.
After presentation of the whole team and discuss with skaeholder, we continue
with the polygon-shaped 'dot' logo :)
